OL,11,G0010F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics treat a woman who is
OL,13,     Gin agony with a slipped disc, a
OL,14,     Gman with a chronic lung disease
OL,15,     Gwho can hardly breathe, and a
OL,16,     Gpatient who is unresponsive.
